lines.text: You're weird. You're strange. I don't like you.
But did we have a good time here? Hello?
Are we going somewhere? Hello? It's too late. You're my guests.
I tell you what. We'll play a game. Anybody here like games? Hello? Game time!
Are we going somewhere? Hello? It's too late, you're my guests. And by the way, didn't I tell you I wasn't alone? Meet the family.
